HLTH_INTAKE_ELIMINATION.EVENT_DATE >= #ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.HEALTH_TRACKING_START_DD_MON_YYYY AND HLTH_INTAKE_ELIMINATION.EVENT_DATE <= SYSDATE AND HLTH_INTAKE_ELIMINATION.TEST = 0 AND HLTH_INTAKE_ELIMINATION.STATUS = 0
CASE WHEN @{R0} IS NULL OR @{R1} IS NULL THEN -1 WHEN months_between ( @{R1} , @{R0} ) >= 0 THEN FLOOR ( months_between ( @{R1} , @{R0} ) / 12 ) ELSE -1 END

CASE WHEN DIM_CLIENT.BIRTH_DATE IS NULL OR AGGREGATE_MONTH_LEVEL.EVENT_DATE_MONTH IS NULL THEN -1 WHEN months_between ( AGGREGATE_MONTH_LEVEL.EVENT_DATE_MONTH , DIM_CLIENT.BIRTH_DATE ) >= 0 THEN FLOOR ( months_between ( AGGREGATE_MONTH_LEVEL.EVENT_DATE_MONTH , DIM_CLIENT.BIRTH_DATE ) / 12 ) ELSE -1 END
